citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:34pm on
01-May-18.
Telephone contact was made later in the afternoon. The licensee was working. Alternative dates and times were
provided during the telephone conversation.
